<template>
  <form>
    <label for="new-todo-input"> What needs to be done? </label>
    <input
      type="text"
      id="new-todo-input"
      name="new-todo"
      autocomplete="off" />
    <button type="submit">Add</button>
  </form>
</template>


<script>
  export default {
  methods: {
    onSubmit() {
      console.log("form submitted");
    },
  },
};

</script>
